The sixteen '''[[Mining Guild/Legends|Mining Guild]] elders''' from [[Nar Kreeta]] were sent from the guild to negotiate with a [[Unidentified Hutt crime lord (Nar Kreeta)|local Hutt crimelord]]. The [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]] took them as prisoners and intended to use them in betting matches against a [[Rancor/Legends|rancor]]. [[Kyle Katarn]] and [[Jaden Korr]] were sent to investigate their disappearance, at which time they found and freed the elders.

